10
00:01:26,944 --> 00:01:28,819
You've grown, Tronte.

11
00:01:30,569 --> 00:01:32,110
Do I know you?

12
00:01:33,028 --> 00:01:34,402
I knew your mother.

13
00:01:35,778 --> 00:01:37,235
But that was long ago.

14
00:01:38,403 --> 00:01:40,735
